trans-unit.source: Indicates whether <codeEntityReference>AcquireToken</codeEntityReference> should automatically prompt only if necessary or regardless of whether there is a cached token.
trans-unit.target: Indicates whether <codeEntityReference>AcquireToken</codeEntityReference> should automatically prompt only if necessary or regardless of whether there is a cached token.

trans-unit.source: Acquire token will prompt the user for credentials only when necessary.
trans-unit.target: Acquire token will prompt the user for credentials only when necessary.

trans-unit.source: If a token that meets the requirements is already cached then the user will not be prompted.
trans-unit.target: If a token that meets the requirements is already cached then the user will not be prompted.

trans-unit.source: The user will be prompted for credentials even if there is a token that meets the requirements already in the cache.
trans-unit.target: The user will be prompted for credentials even if there is a token that meets the requirements already in the cache.
